%2C%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20avoid%20situations%20where%20they%20are%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFemale%20students%2C%20it%20said%2C%20must%20refrain%20from%20leaving%20the%20hostel%20or%20lodging%20rooms%20during%20night%20hours%20unless%20absolutely%20necessary%20and%20must%20step%20out%20only%20after%20informing%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAvoid%20going%20off-campus%20during%20late%20or%20odd%20hours.%20All%20Hostel%20borders%20should%20abide%20by%20the%20hostel%20norms%20%26amp%3B%20regulations%20laid%20by%20the%20institute%20and%20administration.%20Be%20cautious%20and%20avoid%20associating%20with%20individuals%20who%20appear%20unknown%20or%20are%20suspicious%20in%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20women%20doctors%20and%20students%20must%20always%20ensure%20they%20have%20a%20means%20of%20making%20emergency%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20on%20duty%20you%20should%20be%20well%20composed%20emotionally%2C%20remain%20alert%20about%20the%20surroundings%20and%20should%20graciously%20interact%20with%20the%20public%2C%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20attract%20unnecessary%20attention%20of%20unscrupulous%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20added%20in%20another%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20said%20students%20and%20women%20doctors%20must%20immediately%20communicate%20any%20grievances%20to%20internal%20committees%20to%20address%20harassment%20or%20ragging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20said%20it%20had%20been%20issued%20in%20the%20greater%20interest%20of%20doctors%2C%20students%20and%20staff%20members%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20on%20campus%2C%20with%20the%20students%20saying%20that%20authorities%20should%20improve%20security%20arrangements%20instead%20of%20telling%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Association%20o