e%20case%20was%20registered%2C%20was%20not%20tenable%20in%20law%20and%20smacked%20of%20mala%20fide%2C%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20told%20the%20court.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20have%20filed%20for%20interim%20bail.%20He%20will%20easily%20pass%20the%20triple%20test%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20interim%20relief.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20say%20interim%20bail%2C%20we%20will%20not%20give%20interim%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20August%205%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20said%20there%20was%20no%20malice%20in%20the%20acts%20of%20the%20CBI%20and%20that%20the%20agency%20had%20demonstrated%20how%20the%20AAP%20leader%20could%20influence%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%2C%20introduced%20in%20November%202021%2C%20was%20withdrawn%20in%20September%20next%20year%20amid%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20policy.%20The%20CBI%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20have%20alleged%20that%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20among%20others%2C%20committed%20irregularities%20and%20extended%20undue%20favours%20to%20licence%20holders%20after%20the%20new%20policy%20was%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20corruption%20cases%20linked%20to%20the%20liquor%20policy.%20They%20are%20currently%20out%20on%20bail.%20AAP%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20of%20political%20vendetta%20and%20trashed%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20its%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723617900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fuvpg58v8_arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-bail-for-delhi-chi