ired%20Laxman%20Narasimhan%20A%20Year%20After%20His%20Appointment%20As%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20Brian%20Niccol%2C%20chief%20executive%20at%20Chipotle%2C%20would%20be%20the%20coffee%20chain's%20new%20CEO%20--%20just%20over%20a%20year%20after%20current%20boss%20Laxman%20Narasimhan%20took%20over%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarasimhan%20steps%20down%20as%20chief%20executive%20and%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Starbucks%20board%20%26quot%3Bwith%20immediate%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20company%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20shares%20were%20around%2021%20percent%20higher%20in%20early%20afternoon%20trading%2C%20while%20Chipotle%20Mexican%20Grill%20shares%20fell%20by%20about%20eight%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leadership%20shifts%20come%20as%20Starbucks%20pushes%20to%20turn%20around%20its%20business%2C%20while%20contending%20with%20broad-based%20sales%20declines%20in%20its%20most%20recent%20financial%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20saw%20a%20bruising%20April%20earnings%20report%2C%20battering%20its%20shares%20and%20prompting%20Narasimhan%20to%20promise%20a%20reset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20previously%20cited%20weakening%20consumer%20sentiment%20and%20tough%20market%20conditions%20in%20China%20as%20factors%20in%20its%20troubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20been%20contending%20with%20pressure%20from%20activist%20fund%20Elliott%20Investment%20Management%2C%20which%20took%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20chain%20and%20had%20been%20seeking%20ways%20to%20boost%20the%20share%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coffee%20giant%20is%20working%20meanwhile%20to%20finalize%20contracts%20with%20unionized%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELynne%20Fox%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Workers%20United%20union%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20continuing%20to%20work%20with%20Starbucks%20to%20resolve%20massive%20outstanding%20litigation%20and%20reach%20fair%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20replacement%20of%20Laxman%20Narasimhan%20as%20Starbucks%20CEO%20is%20the%20result%20of%20growing%20dissatisfaction%2C%20particularly%20from%20activist%20investors%2C%20over%20the%20way%20the%20chain%20has%20been%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neil%20Saunders%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20GlobalData%2C%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20some%20of%20the%20slowdown%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20a%20more%20sluggish%20consumer%20cutting%20back%2C%20much%20is%20also%20the%20result%20of%20a%20worsening%20store%20experience%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20innovation%20in%20areas%20like%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20could%20be%20hoping%20for%20improvements%20in%20day-to-day%20operations%20by%20bringing%20Niccol%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrian%20is%20a%20culture%20carrier%20who%20brings%20a%20wealth%20of%20experience%20and%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20driving%20innovation%20and%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Starbucks%20board%20chair%20Mellody%20Hobson%20in%20a%20statement%20as%20the%20company%20announced%20the%20leadership%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiccol%20has%20served%20as%20Chipotle's%20CEO%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20naming%20him%20Starbucks'%20new%20CEO%2C%20the%20company%20noted%20that%20his%20work%20at%20Chipotle%20had%20%26quot%3Bdriven%20significant%20growth%20and%20value%20creation%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20revenue%20that%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20and%20higher%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarasimhan%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20PepsiCo%20and%20other%20consumer%20brands%2C%20had%20taken%20over%20the%20top%20spot%20in%202023%20after%20a%20period%20working%20with%20longtime%20Starbucks%20CEO%20and%20interim%20boss%20Howard%20Schultz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20noted%20that%20Narasimhan%2C%20during%20his%20tenure%2C%2