or%20said%20it%20is%20tragic%20to%20see%20what%20was%20hailed%20as%20a%20democratic%20revolution%20degenerating%20into%20anarchy%2C%20and%20violence%20targeting%20the%20minorities%20and%20the%20Hindu%20minority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20extremely%20tragic%20that%20what%20was%20hailed%20as%20a%20democratic%2C%20popular%20revolution%20has%20degenerated%20into%20anarchy%2C%20and%20violence%20targeting%20the%20minorities%20and%20the%20Hindu%20minority...%20We%20in%20India%20must%20stand%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh.%20But%20it's%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20be%20indifferent%20when%20every%20symbol%20of%20India's%20friendship%20with%20Bangladesh%20is%20being%20attacked%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20how%20several%20institutions%20were%20vandalised%20during%20the%20ongoing%20violence%2C%20making%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20negative%26quot%3B%20sign%20for%20people%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20statue%20of%20the%20surrender%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20forces%20to%20Indian%20soldiers%20has%20been%20smashed%20to%20bits.%20The%20Indian%20Cultural%20Centre%20is%20destroyed%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20institutions%20are%20vandalised%2C%20including%20the%20ISKCON%20temple.%20All%20of%20these%20things%20are%20very%20negative%20signs%20for%20people%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20not%20in%20Bangladesh's%20interest%20either%20to%20come%20across%20in%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20be%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20about%20the%20restoration%20of%20their%20democracy%2C%20but%20in%20the%20process%2C%20you%20turn%20against%20the%20minorities%20and%20in%20particular%20one%20minority%2C%20inevitably%2C%20that%20will%20be%20noticed%20and%20resented%20in%20our%20country%20and%20elsewhere...%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20experiencing%20a%20volatile%20political%20situation%2C%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20resigned%20f