n-translation-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpanish%20is%20the%20most%20common%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20almost%20everyone%20is%20bilingual%2C%20Catalan%20is%20the%20main%20language%20outside%20Barcelona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Catalan%20words%20are%20the%20same%20or%20close%20enough%20to%20Spanish%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bhola%26quot%3B%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bhola%26quot%3B%20while%20%26quot%3Badi%C3%B3s%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Bad%C3%A9u%26quot%3B%20(ad-ay-oo).%20But%20you'd%20never%20guess%20others%2C%20like%20strawberry%20is%20%26quot%3Bfresa%26quot%3B%20in%20Spanish%20but%20%26quot%3Bmaduixa%26quot%3B%20(mad-oo-sha)%20in%20Catalan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20here%2C%20you're%20expected%20to%20speak%20Catalan%2C%20though%20many%20foreigners%20don't.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-men-without-kids-no-fathers-less-complicated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20boys%2C%20my%20children%20have%20only%20two%20hours%20a%20week%20of%20Spanish%20instruction%20in%20school%2C%20and%20the%20default%20for%20all%20school%20communication%20with%20parents%20is%20Catalan.%20I%20regularly%20have%20hybrid%20conversations%20with%20other%20parents%20where%20I%20speak%20Spanish%2C%20and%20they%20respond%20in%20Catalan.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20can%20follow%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20conversation.%20But%20if%20I%20get%20lost%2C%20they'd%20usually%20rather%20switch%20to%20English%20than%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20Catalans%2C%20the%20language%20is%20a%20political%20and%20emotional%20representation%20of%20cultural%20identity%2C%20not%20just%20a%20communication%20tool.%20Catalan%20independence%20is%20a%20heated%20topic%20since%20the%202017%20independence%20referendum%2C%20which%20Spain%20declared%20illegal.%20Instead%20of%20ignoring%20it%2C%20the%20police%20used%20force%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20the%20parents%20of%20my%20children's%20friends%20feel%20so%20strongly%20about%20what%20the%20language%20represents.%20The%20school%20my%20kids%20attend%20in%20Girona%20was%20a%20polling%20station%20and%20TV%20footage%20of%20the%20violence%20at%20the%20gates%20there%20circulated%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Catalan%20paella%20with%20prawns%20and%20lemon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b9a6265da406397bf4dfcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECatalan%20paella%20is%20different%20from%20what%20you%20find%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3Cp%3ENicola%20Prentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205c68a24-1d15-4c09-8f2c-1a01fc9f5c13%5C%22%3E2.%20The%20paella%20looks%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20not%20being%20a%20seafood%20fan%2C%20I%20love%20paella%20because%20I%20can%20just%20pick%20out%20the%20prawns%20and%20mussels.%20Until%20I%20got%20to%20Catalonia%20and%20discovered%20that%20the%20yellow%20rice%20with%20seafood%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20chicken%20or%20rabbit%20is%20Valencia%20style.%20Catalan%20paella%20is%20dark%20brown%20in%20color%2C%20much%20more%20seafood%20heavy%2C%20and%20never%20contains%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20Catalan%20version%20of%20paella%20made%20with%20short%20noodles%20(fideua)%20and%20served%20with%20aioli%20(garlic%20mayo)%20or%20the%20dramatic%20squid%20ink%20dish%20(arroz%20negro).%20My%20children%20call%20it%20Halloween%20Rice%20because%20it%20stains%20their%20teeth%2C%20tongues%2C%20and%20everything%20else%2C%20black.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20bottles%20of%20sparkling%20wine%20in%20Catalonia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b9a6db5da406397bf4dfd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECatalonia%20is%20home%20to%20Cava%2C%20Spain's%20sparkling%20wine.%3Cp%3ENicola%20Prentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d45f14e-6195-4185-a1c2-5e6bae508227%5C%22%3E3.%20You'll%20want%20to%20branch%20out%20into%20Catalan%20wines%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20think%20of%20rioja%20when%20they%20think%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-underrated-wine-regions-to-visit-around-world-from-sommelier-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpanish%20wine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20I%20can%20certainly%20drink%20wines%20from%20La%20Rioja%20in%20Catalonia%2C%20the%20waiter%20is%20much%20friendlier%20if%20I%20ask%20for%20Catalan%20wines.%20An%20award-winning%20local%20sommelier%20once%20told%20me%20rioja%20is%20only%20famous%20because%20it%20was%20the%20favorite%20wine%20of%20Franco%2C%20the%20Spanish%20dictator%20who%20ruled%20from%201938%20to%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20that's%20the%20real%20reason%20or%20not%2C%20local%20is%20king%2C%20so%20you'll%20be%20recommended%20wine%20from%20the%20Pened%C3%A8s%20if%20you're%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20from%20Priorat%20in%20Tarragona%2C%20and%20from%20the%20L'Empord%C3%A0%20in%20Girona.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Catalonia%20is%20also%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fbest-champagne%23best-cava-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECava%20%E2%80%94%20Spain's%20sparkling%20wine%3C%2Fa%3E%20similar%20to%20Champagne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20people%20dancing%20sardana%20in%20Catalonia%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bad554b4912df3ae1b055f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYoung%20and%20old%20people%20come%20together%20to%20dance%20the%20Sardana.%3Cp%3ENicola%20Prentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fef5f04a-b53b-4354-b3b3-a59235e02aae%5C%22%3E4.%20Th