2027%2C%20who%20left%20Singapore's%20public%20healthcare%20system%20and%20is%20now%20working%20as%20a%20locum%20doctor.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%2013%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20parents%2C%20who%20are%20doctors%20too.%20My%20parents%20find%20great%20fulfillment%20in%20their%20profession.%20Even%20though%20they've%20been%20practicing%20medicine%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20they%20still%20love%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20also%20my%20parents%20who%20tried%20to%20dissuade%20me%20from%20pursuing%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%20They%20told%20me%20some%20horror%20stories%20about%20what%20being%20a%20doctor%20was%20really%20like%20and%20warned%20me%20about%20how%20taxing%20it%20could%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20remained%20deeply%20inspired%20by%20their%20careers%20and%20decided%20to%20press%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22057884fe-aeb2-4118-83a4-7e24bf33ddff%5C%22%3EMedical%20school%20was%20fun%20but%20grueling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Faith%20Choo%20(right)%20and%20her%20best%20friend%20(left)%20in%20their%20graduation%20gowns.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b21b516c8f0a134f79e4a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChoo%20(right)%20graduated%20from%20medical%20school%20in%202021.%3Cp%3EFaith%20Choo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two%20years%20of%20medical%20school%20felt%20like%20high%20school%20all%20over%20again.%20There%20was%20lots%20of%20studying%20as%20well%20as%20material%20to%20memorize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20got%20a%20lot%20more%20exciting%20but%20taxing%20from%20the%20third%20year%20onwards.%20That%20was%20when%20we%20got%20to%20shadow%20junior%20doctors%20at%20the%20hospital.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20spend%20full%20working%20days%20in%20the%20hospital%20before%20going%20home%20to%20study%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20dawned%20upon%20me%20then%20that%20we%20would%20be%20taking%20over%20from%20those%20junior%20doctors%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20The%20burden%20and%20responsibility%20of%20having%20to%20take%20care%20of%20patients%20began%20to%20weigh%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20our%20seniors%20in%20medical%20school%20would%20warn%20us%20about%20life%20after%20graduation.%20They%20would%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20terrible%20working%20hours%20that%20came%20with%20being%20on%20call%2C%20like%20having%20to%20work%20for%20two%20days%20straight%20without%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20to%20worry%20if%20I%20could%20live%20up%20to%20the%20challenge.%20I%20remembered%20asking%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20I%20physically%20cope%20with%20this%3F%20Can%20I%20mentally%20step%20up%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20challenge%3F%20Do%20I%20have%20the%20resilience%20and%20skills%20required%20to%20do%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ed811d4-3c8e-43dc-a69f-33e37017a9e8%5C%22%3EConfronting%20the%20long%20hours%20and%20feelings%20of%20burnout%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Faith%20Choo%20sitting%20at%20her%20desk%20with%20her%20stethoscope%20and%20medical%20devices%20sprawled%20across%20the%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb1c4bb4912df3ae1b08af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChoo%20first%20thought%20about%20leaving%20the%20public%20healthcare%20system%20after%20she%20clocked%2019%20consecutive%20days%20of%20work%20in%20the%20hospital.%3Cp%3EFaith%20Choo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20college%2C%20I%20did%20hospital%20attachments%20and%20worked%20with%20general%20practitioners%20at%20their%20clinics.%20But%20even%20that%20wasn't%20able%20to%20give%20me%20a%20full%20taste%20of%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20transition%20that%20came%20after%20graduation%20was%20the%20long%20hours.%20It%20wasn't%20long%20before%20the%20exacting%20routine%2C%20manpower%20constraints%2C%20and%20feelings%20of%20burnout%20began%20to%20pile%20up%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thought%20of%20leaving%20first%20crossed%20my%20mind%20after%20I%20clocked%2019%20consecutive%20days%20of%20work%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20are%20more%20tired%20than%20the%20patients%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Even%20the%20patients%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20rest%2C%20but%20for%20doctors%2C%20when%20you're%20on%20a%20call%2C%20you%20have%20to%20make%20life%20and%20death%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20still%20held%20to%20a%20high%20level%20of%20accountability%20and%20you%20want%20to%20do%20the%20best%20for%20your%20patients%2C%20but%20you%20physically%20can't%20because%20you%20are%20just%20so%20exhausted%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20then%20that%20such%20a%20job%20wouldn't%20be%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9359a95-2687-4c13-b021-1daaf23c14a7%5C%22%3ELife%20as%20a%20medical%20graduate%20in%20Singapore%20ain't%20easy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Singapore.%20our%20medical%20education%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moh.gov.sg%2Fhpp%2Fall-healthcare-professionals%2Fcareer-practice%2FCareerNPracticesDetails%2Fmedical-dental-undergraduate-agreement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavily%20subsidized%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20government.%20After%20graduation%2C%20students%20have%20to%20fulfil%20a%20service%20bond%20of%20five%20years.%20This%20is%20on%20top%20of%20the%20one%20year%20of%20housemanship%20that%20takes%20place%20right%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJunior%20doctors%20could%20put%20in%20about%2060%20hours%20of%20work%20in%20a%20good%20week%2C%20though%20that