tors'%20Association%20(FORDA)%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20call%20off%20the%20strike%20was%20taken%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20that%20their%20demands%20had%20been%20met%2C%20including%20one%20seeking%20an%20assurance%20that%20the%20Central%20Healthcare%20Protection%20Act%20would%20be%20passed%20to%20curb%20attacks%20on%20medical%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20FORDA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20requested%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20will%20be%20part%20of%20a%20committee%20on%20the%20Central%20Healthcare%20Protection%20Act%2C%20work%20on%20which%20will%20start%20within%2015%20days.%20It%20said%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20call%20off%20the%20strike%20on%C2%A0Wednesday%20morning%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20patient%20welfare.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2011%20pm%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20FORDA%20statement%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20Mr%20Nadda%20has%20welcomed%20the%20organisation's%20decision%20and%20all%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20safety%20of%20healthcare%20workers%20would%20be%20addressed.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnion%20Health%20Minister%2C%20Shri%20%40JPNadda%20met%20with%20the%20Federation%20of%20Resident%20Doctors%20Association%20(%40FordaIndia)%20delegation%20today.%20%C2%A0He%20welcomed%20their%20decision%20to%20call%20off%20the%20strike%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20and%20assured%20them%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20will%20address%20all%20their%20concerns%20to%20ensure%20a%20safer%20and%20better%20work%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUnion%20Health%20Minister%2C%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJPNadda%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40JPNadda%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20with%20the%20Federation%20of%20Resident%20Doctors%20Association%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFordaIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40FordaIndia%3C%2Fa%3E)%20delegation%20today.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20welcomed%20their%20decision%20to%20call%20off%20the%20strike%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20and%20assured%20them%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20will%20address%20all%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRqheiRVF1d%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRqheiRVF1d%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20(%40MoHFW_INDIA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoHFW_INDIA%2Fstatus%2F1823411474607247385%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiffering%20with%20FORDA%2C%20the%20Federation%20of%20All%20India%20Medical%20Association%20(FAIMA)%20said%20most%20of%20the%20resident%20doctors'%20associations%20(RDAs)%20are%20with%20it%20and%20would%20continue%20the%20strike%20along%20with%20FAIMA%20and%20AIIMS%20Delhi.%20It%20said%20a%20national%20RDA%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20over%2090%20representatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20RDA%20of%20AIIMS%20said%20the%20strike%20would%20continue%20until%20they%20got%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20assurance%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20through%20strict%20laws%20like%20the%20Central%20Healthcare%20Protection%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AIIMS%20RDA%20will%20continue%20their%20indefinite%20strike%2C%20including%20the%20suspension%20of%20academic%20activities%2C%20elective%20OPDs%2C%20ward%20services%2C%20and%20OT%20services.%20However%2C%20emergency%20services%2C%20ICUs%20and%20emergency%20OT%20will%20remain%20operational%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20association%20posted%20on%20its%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAIIMS%20RDA%20and%20other%20RDAs%20will%20continue%20the%20strike%20till%20we%20get%20complete%20assurance%20on%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20doctors%20nationwide%20through%20strict%20laws%20that%20is%20CPA%20(central%20protection%20act)%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Resident%20Doctors%20of%20Maharashtra%20(MARD)%20and%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Associations%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20also%20said%20they%20would%20not%20call%20off%20the%20strike%20as%20did%20associations%20in%20AIIMS%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Rishikesh%20and%20Mangalagiri%2C%20National%20Institute%20of%20Mental%20Health%20and%20Neurosciences%20(NIMHANS)%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20PGI%20Chandigarh%2C%20JIPMER%2C%20SGPGI%20Lucknow%2C%20IMS%20BHU%2C%20ESIC%20Joka%20and%20KGMU%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Resident%20Doctors'%20Association%20of%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%20also%20said%20it%20would%20continue%20the%20strike.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20it%20said%20that%20is%20no%20longer%20associated%20with%20FORDA%20and%20would%20hold%20a%20meeting%20at%209%20am%20to%20discuss%20the%20plan%20of%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20began%20on%20Monday%2C%20three%20days%20after%20the%20body%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20post-graduate%20trainee%2C%20who%20was%20working%20at%20Kolkata's%20renowned%20state%20government-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20was%20found%20inside%20a%20seminar%20hall%20in%20the%20institution.%20She%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%2C%20and%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20working%20with%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20sexual%20assault%2C%20the%20trainee%20doctor's%20post-mortem%20report%20revealed%20that%20several%20injuries%20were%20inflicted%20on%20her%20before%20she%20was%20smothered%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20had%20demanded%20that%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20was%20met%20on%20Tuesday%20through%20a%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order.%20An%20assurance%20on%20the%20Act%20remained%20a%20hurdle%2C%20however%2C%20and%20FORDA%20had%20also%20posted%20around%206.30%20pm%20that%20the%20strike%20would%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20assurance%20on%20Central%20Healthcare%20Protection%20Act%20-%20No%20call%20off!%20OUR%20DEMANDS%20still%20stand%20incomplete%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20several%20cities%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Kolkata%2C%20and%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20strike%2C%20doctors%20had%20said%20all%20elective%20services%20would%20be%20halted.%20Patients%20were%20affected%20in%20many%20hospitals%2C%20including%20some%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20videos%20emerged%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-rg-kar-college-video-patients-bang-opd-doors-doctors-raise-justice-slogans-in-up-6326079%5C%22%3Ebanging%20on%20the%20doors%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20treatment%20as%20they%20had%20travelled%20from%20different%20cities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComprehensive%20Framework%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Healthcare%20Protection%20Act%20has%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20doctors%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20have%20sought%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20bill%20which%20provides%20a%20comprehensive%20framework%20as%20well%20as%20severe%20penalties%20for%20those%20who%20assault%20or%20intimidate%20doctors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20inclusions%20in%20the%20bill%2C%20the%20doctors%20want%20swift%20investigation%20and%20prosecution%20of%20such%20cases%20and%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20committees%20in%20each%20hospital%20to%20tackle%20violence%20against%20medical%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2019%20states%20have%20enacted%20legislation%20to%20protect%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20beginning%20with%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%202007%2C%20the%20doctors%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20central%20Act%20to%20ensure%20uniformity%20as%20well%20as%20protection%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20was%20initially%20sparked%20by%20attacks%20on%20doctors%20by%20relatives%20of%20patients%20who%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20not%20given%20proper%20healthcare%20and%20blamed%20poor%20outcomes%20on%20negligence%20by%20medical%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20taken%20place%20over%20the%20issue%20several%20times%20and%2C%20during%20the%20latest%20agitation%2C%20the%20doctors%20also%20asked%20for%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20fast-track%20courts%20to%20bring%20the%20guilty%20to%20book%20in%20cases%20of%20violence%20against%20healthcare%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723579560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F8j5c1dl_doctors-_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-doctors-body-calls-off-strike-over-kolkata-doctors-rape-murder-after-meeting-with-health-minister-jp-nadda-6331084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20stating%20that%20the%20strike%20which%20began%20after%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%20will%20continue%2C%20a%20key%20doctors'%20body%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20that%20the%20agitation%20will%20be%20called%20off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-doctors-body-calls-off-strike-over-kolkata-doctors-rape-murder-after-meeting-with-health-minister-jp-nadda-6331084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blake%20Lively%20Addresses%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Narrative%20From%20%E2%80%98It%20Ends%20With%20Us%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723578842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDF-06827_r-1.jpg%3